  "title": "Retail Assistant (Bakery Stall | Old Airport Road | 5 Days Work Week)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Basic $ 2000 to $ 2200</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: Oil Airport Road, Singapore</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: 11am to 8pm</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working days: Wednesday to Sunday (Mon &amp; Tue off)</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist customers with purchases and provide friendly service</li>\n  <li>Handle cash and operate POS/cash register</li>\n  <li>Pack, label, and display bakery items neatly</li>\n  <li>Ensure cleanliness of counter and work area</li>\n  <li>Assist in stock checking and replenishment</li>\n  <li>Follow hygiene and food safety guidelines</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>No experience required (training provided)</li>\n  <li>Friendly, polite, and customer-oriented</li>\n  <li>Able to work in a fast-paced environment</li>\n  <li>Willing to work weekends and public holidays</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
